### 4.3 分析器加载机制（SPI）

Dependency-Check 使用 Java SPI（Service Provider Interface）机制动态加载所有分析器：

**配置文件**：`META-INF/services/org.owasp.dependencycheck.analyzer.Analyzer`

```
# 文件中列出了所有 Analyzer 实现类的全限定名
org.owasp.dependencycheck.analyzer.JarAnalyzer
org.owasp.dependencycheck.analyzer.CentralAnalyzer
org.owasp.dependencycheck.analyzer.CPEAnalyzer
org.owasp.dependencycheck.analyzer.NvdCveAnalyzer
...
```

**加载流程**（AnalyzerService.java）：

```java
public List<Analyzer> getAnalyzers(List<AnalysisPhase> phases) {
    final List<Analyzer> analyzers = new ArrayList<>();
    final Iterator<Analyzer> iterator = service.iterator();
    while (iterator.hasNext()) {
        final Analyzer a = iterator.next();
        // 1. 按阶段过滤
        if (!phases.contains(a.getAnalysisPhase())) continue;
        // 2. 实验性分析器默认不加载
        if (!experimentalEnabled && a.getClass().isAnnotationPresent(Experimental.class)) continue;
        // 3. 已退休分析器默认不加载
        if (!retiredEnabled && a.getClass().isAnnotationPresent(Retired.class)) continue;
        analyzers.add(a);
    }
    return analyzers;
}
```

